name: Rescue of Blondell
overview: Rescue of Blondell is a simple horizontal scrolling shooter in which your character is a wizard on a magic carpet and you must shoot at evil demonic birds. Originally published in COMPUTE! 1985/01 (Issue #56) it was also published in Italy by Gruppo Editoriale Jackson in Super VIC & C64 A2-N05 (May 1985)
